## Description {#details}

Class the provides an iterator over the memory64 memory ranges.

Only the the first descriptor is validated as readable beforehand.

Definition at line 158 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/minidump-h">Minidump.h</a>.
